      • addWord

        public void addWord(java.lang.String word)
        This method checks if the word passed is in the stop words. list, if so it will be ignored by the application. If the word is not in the stop words list it will be added to the image generator map.
        Parameters:
        word - The word to be stored and used in image generation.

        This method initializes / creates the word cloud image.
        Parameters:
        imageOption - The option controlling image configuration - 0, 1 and 2 options available.
